  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You ready yourself for combat and steel your mind for battle.</p><p>For the duration of this Jutsu, while not wearing armor, your AC is 10 + your Constitution Modifier + your Taijutsu or Ninjutsu ability modifier. If your Constitution or Taijutsu or Ninjutsu ability modifiers are above 20 (+5), they are treated as being 20 (+5) for the purposes of this Jutsu instead.</p><p><strong>Empower:</strong> While this Jutsu is active, as a reaction to a creature making an attack roll against you, you may expend a Ki Die to increase your AC by 2 against the triggering attack.</p>",
